    metaDescription: "How to set up your motorcycle suspension for touring with luggage. Preload, sag, and damping adjustments for loaded riding on UK roads.",
    heroImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80",
    author: "VisorUp Team",
