    title: "Motorcycle Windscreen and Wind Protection Guide",
    metaDescription: "How to choose the right windscreen for motorcycle touring. Height, width, and material options to improve comfort on long UK rides.",
    heroImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474524955719-b9f5b519e4d6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80",
    author: "VisorUp Team",
    publishDate: "2026-05-06",
    readTime: "6 min read",
