    title: "Heated Grips, Seats, and Comfort Upgrades for Touring",
    metaDescription: "Essential comfort upgrades for touring motorcycles. Heated grips, gel seats, bar risers, and accessories that transform long-distance riding.",
    heroImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477959858617-67f85cf4f1df?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80",
    author: "VisorUp Team",
