<p>If you regularly tour with a pillion, the bike choice should consider their comfort as much as yours. A cramped, vibrating perch with minimal grab rails and no wind protection will ensure your pillion never wants to tour again. The best pillion bikes provide genuine rear comfort that makes two-up touring a pleasure for both rider and passenger.</p>
